text = "Ferry CLEAN plates to the kitchen pass - the chef flashes red when he's starving
Grab a BUS TUB (empty hands), scoop dirty plates in, dump at the pit (E / Square)
Then run the machine (E / Square) - clean plates come out the far end
LMB/R1 grab-drop-scoop, RMB/L1 throw, sticks or WASD+mouse, Esc frees the mouse
Clean plates that touch the floor get dirty. Hard throws break plates. Forever."

